Trips
Search for available trips based on criteria.

query.description: The airport code for the departure location.
The airport code for the arrival location.
Type of the flight. Must be one of: 'one-way', 'roundtrip'.
The number of results to return per page. Minimum: 1, Maximum: 100.
An optional filter to search flights by specific airlines.
An optional filter for the maximum duration of flights in minutes.
An optional filter for the maximum price of flights.
An optional sorting parameter. Must be one of: 'price', 'duration'.

request.description:
This endpoint provides a way to search for available flights based on a set of criteria
such as departure and arrival locations, flight type, and other optional parameters.
